Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.95,0:02:22.62,Shinsou credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad (4000,0)\c&H0100BE&}Shinsou uvádí{\c&HF3F1FF&}\NPřeklad: Kataro\NKorektura: Spageta9
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.69,0:00:08.11,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm gonna go to the city!}Pojedu do města!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:12.01,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm gonna go to my uncle's farm and \Nhelp one of the cows give birth.}Pojedu pomoct s porodem jedné krávy na strýčkovu farmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:13.45,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm going all by myself, too!}Také pojedu úplně sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:16.18,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{And once I'm done helping,}A jakmile mu pomůžu,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:20.82,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{I can go shopping in the city.\NMy mom gave me some money.}Můžu jít nakupovat do města. \NMaminka mi dala nějaké peníze.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.59,0:00:23.77,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{I wonder what I should buy.}Zajímalo by mě, co bych si měla koupit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:26.77,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Is there anything you want? \NI'll buy you something.}Je něco co bys chtěl? Koupím ti něco.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.77,0:00:27.77,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{No.}Ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.07,0:00:31.02,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{There must be something. I mean—}Musí být něco. Přece—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:32.92,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{I told you, I don't want anything.}Řekl jsem, že nic nechci.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:35.63,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Why do you have to say it like that?}Proč tak mluvíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.96,0:00:40.89,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{I just wanted to buy you something \Nsince you've never been to the city...}Jen jsem ti chtěla něco koupit,\N když jsi ještě nikdy nebyl ve městě...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:44.94,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Shut up! Just go to the city or wherever!}Zmlkni! Prostě jeď do města nebo kamkoliv!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:46.62,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Why are you getting mad?}Proč jsi naštvaný?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:47.78,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm not mad!}Nejsem!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:48.90,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Yes, you are!}Ale jsi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:49.90,Shinsou main,Older sis,0000,0000,0000,,{Now, now.}No tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:53.09,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Sis...}Sestři...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:54.74,Shinsou main,Older sis,0000,0000,0000,,{You shouldn't be fighting.}Neměli byste se hádat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.31,0:00:57.07,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{We're not fighting.}Nehádáme se.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.63,0:00:58.59,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Right?}Že jo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.59,0:00:59.91,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Y-Yeah...}J-Jo...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:01.89,Shinsou main,Older sis,0000,0000,0000,,{What happened?}Stalo se něco?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.89,0:01:03.29,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{It's nothing.}Nic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:05.44,Shinsou main,Older sis,0000,0000,0000,,{All right, then.}Potom je to tedy v pořádku.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.55,0:01:11.53,Shinsou main,Cow girl Mom,0000,0000,0000,,{Please take care of her.}Prosím, postarej se o ní.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.53,0:01:12.46,Shinsou main,Cow girl uncle,0000,0000,0000,,{I will.}Postarám.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:16.53,Shinsou main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,{How long are you going to keep pouting?}Jak dlouho se budeš takhle tvářit?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.47,Shinsou main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,{Weren't you looking forward \Nto going to the city?}Netěšila ses snad na cestu do města?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:22.34,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{I wanted to go with him...}Chtěla jsem jet s ním...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:27.17,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{But since he couldn't come,\NI wanted to buy him something,}Ale jelikož nemohl jet, tak jsem mu chtěla něco koupit,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.77,0:01:29.77,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{and then he got really angry...}a on se potom hrozně naštval...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.11,0:01:33.02,Shinsou main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm sure he wanted to come, too.}Jsem si jistý, že chtěl jet taky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.02,0:01:34.34,Shinsou main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,{Think about how he feels.}Pochop jak se cítí.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.51,0:01:37.15,Shinsou main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,{Did you two make up?}Udobřili jste se?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:40.76,Shinsou main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,{You should, once you get back.}Měli byste, až se vrátíš.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:46.61,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{I wanted to make up with him.\N I wanted to apologize.}Chtěla jsem se s ním udobřit. \NChtěla jsem se mu omluvit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:51.25,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{But saying "I'm sorry"...}Ale říct "Promiň" ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:57.66,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{is hard, even now.}je těžké, i teď.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:46.08,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Good morning!}Dobré ráno!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:48.67,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{I see you're an early riser, as always.}Koukám, že jsi ranní ptáče, jako vždy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:49.56,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah.}Jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:51.33,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{It's such a nice day today.}Dneska je moc pěkně.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:53.70,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{The sun's so bright!}Slunce tak svítí!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:54.75,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah.}Jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:57.24,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Is my uncle already up?}Je můj strýček vzhůru?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:03:58.13,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't know.}Nevím.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:02.51,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{I see. I'm pretty sure he'll be up soon, though.}Aha. Určitě taky brzo vstane.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:03.64,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{I see.}Chápu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:05.33,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{You must be hungry.}Musíš být hladový.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:08.27,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll go get breakfast ready, \Nso let's eat together.}Připravím snídaní, takže se najíme spolu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:09.26,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Okay.}Dobře.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:16.23,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{He always checks to see if there \Nare any footprints at dawn.}Každé ráno za svítání kontroluje stopy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:19.23,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{The goblins move around at night.}Goblini se pohybují v noci.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.64,0:04:21.95,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{They return to their nests in the morning,}Vrací se do svých hnízd v dopoledních hodinách,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.95,0:04:24.96,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{but they always scout before attacking.}ale před útokem vždy obhlíží okolí.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:29.48,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{He told me that those are the \Nfootprints he's looking for.}Řekl mi, že přesně takové stopy hledá.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:32.96,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{If he doesn't find any footprints,}Když nenajde žádné stopy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:37.67,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{he then carefully checks the fence to \Nsee if any part is loose or damaged.}potom opatrně zkontroluje plot, \Njestli nějaká část z něj není poškozená nebo nechybí.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:40.45,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{f any parts are broken,}Pokud je nějaká část rozbitá,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:44.52,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{he gets out some wood and a stake to fix it.}najde nějaké dřevo a spraví to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:48.43,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{This hasn't changed since \Nhe came here five years ago.}To se nezměnilo od doby,\N co k nám před pěti lety přišel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:50.32,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{It's his daily routine.}Je to jeho denní rutina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:54.44,Ep_Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4.5\fad(276,1)}{Goblin Slayer}Zabiják Goblinů
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:54.04,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Here you go!}Tady to je!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.91,Shinsou main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,{It smells great, as usual. Let's eat.}Voní to skvěle, jako vždy. Dobrou chuť.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:04:59.91,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Let's eat!}Dobrou chuť!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:04.99,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Well? Is it good?}No? Je to dobré?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:05.99,Shinsou main,Goblin Slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah.}Jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:08.96,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Here.}Tady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:10.97,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{It's what I owe you for this month.}Co dlužím za tento měsíc.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:16.65,Shinsou main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,{It's pretty heavy.}Je to dost těžké.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:19.63,Shinsou main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,{I guess being an adventurer \Nis pretty lucrative.}Hádám, že být dobrodruhem je dost výdělečné.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:22.30,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{I've had a lot of work lately.}Poslední dobou mám hodně práce.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:23.80,Shinsou main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,{I see.}Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:28.04,Shinsou main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,{Say, um... Are you going again today?}Pověz... Vyrážíš i dnes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:31.93,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Yes. I'm going to the guild. \NThere's plenty of work there.}Ano. Půjdu do cechu. \NMěla by tam být spousta práce.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:34.68,Shinsou main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,{I see. Don't push yourself too hard.}Chápu. Netlač na sebe tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:35.59,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Yes, sir.}Ano, pane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:39.94,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Hey, I need to make some deliveries. \NWe should go together.}Tak můžeme jít společně, mám taky pár pochůzek.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:41.82,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Sure.}Jistě.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:44.96,Shinsou main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,{Actually, I'll ready a wagon for that.}Potom tedy připravím povoz.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:48.74,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Oh, we'll be fine! \NYou're too protective, Uncle!}Budeme v pořádku strýčku, děláš si zbytečně starosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:52.35,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm stronger than I look, you know.}Jsem silnější než vypadám.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:57.29,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Do you want me to take over?}Chceš se vystřídat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:05:59.93,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Nope! I'm fine.}Ne! Jsem v pohodě.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.93,0:06:00.83,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Okay.}Dobře.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:02.28,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Thanks.}Děkuju.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:03.60,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{It's nothing.}To nic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:06.42,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{How are things lately?}Jak se ti poslední dobou vede?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.98,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{There are more goblins.}Je zde více goblinů.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:09.39,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Really?}Vážně?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:10.77,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Far more than usual.}Mnohem více než obvykle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:12.12,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Are you busy?}Jsi zaneprázdněný?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:12.87,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah.}Jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:15.43,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{You do go out a lot more lately.}Poslední dobou častěji odcházíš.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:16.31,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah.}Jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:19.53,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Having more work is a good thing, though.}Je dobrá věc mít více práce, že.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:20.65,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{No, it's bad.}Ne, je to špatné.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:22.44,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Is it?}Vážně?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:25.28,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{It's better when there are no goblins.}Bez goblinů by to bylo lepší.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:33.20,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{You're right.}Máš pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:36.83,Shinsou main,Mayor,0000,0000,0000,,{You gotta help me out!}Musíte mi pomoct!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:39.28,Shinsou main,Mayor,0000,0000,0000,,{Li'l goblin critters done \Nshowed up in my village!}V mé vesnici se ukázala spousta goblinů.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:43.46,Shinsou main,Mayor,0000,0000,0000,,{They're gunna eat my cows an' burn my fields!}Sežerou mi mé krávy a spálí moje pole!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:45.79,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Ah, so you need an extermination.}Takže je potřebujete zlikvidovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:49.22,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Please submit your form and payment.}Prosím, vyplňte formulář a odevzdejte platbu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:52.00,Shinsou main,Mayor,0000,0000,0000,,{Y-Yes'm. I got 'em right here.}A-Ano. Mám to všechno tady.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:58.29,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Looks like your form is filled out correctly.}Vypadá to, že vaše žádost je v pořádku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:00.85,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll just confirm your payment now.}Ještě potvrdím platbu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:04.69,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Two, four, eight...}Dva, čtyři, osm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:09.25,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{All right, it looks like it's all here.}Tak, všechno vypadá v pořádku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.25,0:07:13.57,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{An adventurer will head out there for \Nthe extermination within a few days.}Během pár dní dorazí dobrodruh zlikvidovat gobliny.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:18.63,Shinsou main,Mayor,0000,0000,0000,,{Is it true that them li'l goblin \Ncritters rape women and eat 'em?}Je pravda, že goblini znásilňují ženy a pak je jí?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:21.75,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{There have indeed been cases like that.}Takové případy se skutečně stávají.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:36.44,Shinsou main,Manager,0000,0000,0000,,{Another goblin-slaying request? \NThat's the third one...}Další žádost o zlikvidování goblinů? \NTo už je třetí...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:37.60,Shinsou main,Manager,0000,0000,0000,,{What's the pay?}Co platba?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:44.54,Shinsou main,Manager,0000,0000,0000,,{That's going to rule out \Nany experienced adventurer.}To vyřazuje zkušené dobrodruhy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:45.88,Shinsou main,Manager,0000,0000,0000,,{Only newbies would...}Pouze nováčci by mohli...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:47.26,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{There is one...}Jeden tu je...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:50.10,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{who's always willing to take care of them...}který je vždy ochoten se o ně postarat ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.75,Shinsou main,Chef,0000,0000,0000,,{Thank you again.}Ještě jednou děkuju.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:54.23,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{No problem! Thank you.}Bez problému! Děkuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:58.52,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm going to get a signature \Nat the reception desk.}Nechám to potvrdit na recepci.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:07:59.49,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{All right.}Dobře.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:03.87,Shinsou main,Spearman,0000,0000,0000,,{So this troll was bearing down on me,}Takže se na mě ten trol řítil,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:08.28,Shinsou main,Spearman,0000,0000,0000,,{but I swung at it like this and dodged \Nits attack just in the nick of time.}ale já jsem se otočil přesně ve chvíli,\N kdy na mě útočil a vyhnul jsem se.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:10.84,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{I see. Well done, sir.}Chápu. Dobrá práce, pane.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:14.72,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{I am very aware that \Ntrolls are powerful foes.}Jsem si vědoma, že jsou trolové silnými protivníky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:18.22,Shinsou main,Spearman,0000,0000,0000,,{I faced a troll with just a single spear.}Čelil jsem trolovi jen s jediným kopím.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:20.60,Shinsou main,Spearman,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't you think I'm amazing?}Nemyslíte, že je to úžasné?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:23.80,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Indeed. If you're feeling tired,}Jistě. Pokud se cítíte unaveně,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:26.11,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{I'd recommend a stamina potion.}mohla bych vám doporučit lektvar výdrže.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:29.57,Shinsou main,spearman,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll take one.}Jeden si vezmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.07,Shinsou main,Spearman,0000,0000,0000,,{The Goblin Slayer...}Zabiják goblinů...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:36.43,Shinsou main,Guy 1,0000,0000,0000,,{That's him?}To je on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:39.45,Shinsou main,Lady 1,0000,0000,0000,,{That's the weirdo who only accepts \Ngoblin-slaying quests, right?}To je ten podivín, který bere jen úkoly \Nna likvidaci goblinů, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:43.72,Shinsou main,Female knight,0000,0000,0000,,{He's a silver rank, just like us?}Má stříbrnou hodnost jako my, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.15,0:08:47.88,Shinsou main,Female knight,0000,0000,0000,,{If all he hunts is weak monsters, who knows \Nif he can even handle bigger prey?}Pokud vše co loví jsou slabá monstra, \Nkdo ví zda by dokázal porazit i silnější?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:50.21,Shinsou main,Female knight,0000,0000,0000,,{Guess they'll let anyone \Nbe silver these days.}Zdá se, že dnes může být na stříbrné hodnosti každý.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:52.84,Shinsou main,Heavy Swordsmant,0000,0000,0000,,{Leave him be. We'll never \Nhave to deal with him.}Nech ho být. Nebudeme se jím zabývat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:58.81,Shinsou main,Rookie Swordsman,0000,0000,0000,,{Look at him. I've never \Nseen such filthy armor.}Podívej se na něj. \NNikdy jsem neviděl tak špinavou zbroj.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:03.27,Shinsou main,Rookie Mage,0000,0000,0000,,{Even our equipment is better than his.}Dokonce i naše vybavení je lepší jak jeho.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:04.23,Shinsou main,Rookie Cleric Warrior,0000,0000,0000,,{Stop it.}Nech toho.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:07.08,Shinsou main,Rookie Cleric Warrior,0000,0000,0000,,{He must be a newbie just like us.}Musí být nováček jako my.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:08.59,Shinsou main,Rookie cleric warrior,0000,0000,0000,,{I'd feel bad if he heard you.}Cítila bych se špatně, kdyby vás slyšel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:12.03,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Good morning, everyone!}Dobré ráno, všem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:14.57,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{It's time to post all the \Nquests available this morning.}Je čas vyvěsit úkoly, které jsou toto ráno k dispozici.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:16.28,Shinsou main,All,0000,0000,0000,,{That's what we've been waiting for!}To je to, na co jsme čekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:17.87,Shinsou main,Guy 4,0000,0000,0000,,{Dragons!}Draci!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:19.55,Shinsou main,Guy 4,0000,0000,0000,,{Is there one for dragon slaying?}Je tam něco se zabíjením draků?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:23.54,Shinsou main,Guy 4,0000,0000,0000,,{I need to gain some more experience \Npoints by doing heroic feats.}Potřebuju získat víc zkušeností tím, \Nže budu dělat hrdinské skutky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:26.16,Shinsou main,Guy 5,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't even try it. \NYou don't have the right equipment.}Ani to nezkoušej. Nemáš na to dostatečné vybavení.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:28.54,Shinsou main,Guy 5,0000,0000,0000,,{Just settle for taking out some bandits.}Prostě se postaráme o nějaké bandity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:29.88,Shinsou main,Guy 5,0000,0000,0000,,{The pay isn't bad, either.}Odměna není špatná.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:32.00,Shinsou main,Greenhorn warrior,0000,0000,0000,,{Quests for porcelain ranks...}Úkoly pro porcelánové hodnosti...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:33.98,Shinsou main,Greenhorn warrior,0000,0000,0000,,{don't pay very much.}neplatí za ně moc.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:36.13,Shinsou main,Greenhorn warrior,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't want to just clean ditches...}Nechci jen umývat nádobí...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:38.79,Shinsou main,Apprentice cleric,0000,0000,0000,,{You can't be too picky.}Nemůžeš být tak vybíravej.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:40.71,Shinsou main,Greenhorn warrior,0000,0000,0000,,{Hey, how about this one?}Hele, co třeba tenhle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:41.64,Shinsou main,Greenhorn warrior,0000,0000,0000,,{Goblin slaying.}Zabíjení goblinů.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.07,0:09:43.93,Shinsou main,Greenhorn warrior,0000,0000,0000,,{That seems made for rookies.}Vypadá to jako něco pro nováčky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:46.84,Shinsou main,Apprentice cleric,0000,0000,0000,,{No way. You heard the Guild Girl.}Zapomeň. Slyšel jsi tu holku z cechu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:49.23,Shinsou main,Apprentice cleric,0000,0000,0000,,{We need to start with the sewers.}Musíme začít ve stokách.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:51.53,Shinsou main,Spearman,0000,0000,0000,,{I can't see! Get out of my way!}Nevidím! Odpal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:53.31,Shinsou main,Heavy swordsman,0000,0000,0000,,{Stop it. Don't push!}Přestaň. Netlač se!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:59.23,Shinsou main,Female knight,0000,0000,0000,,{We're taking this quest. Look somewhere else.}Bereme tenhle úkol. Podívej se po něčem jiném.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:01.91,Shinsou main,Spearman,0000,0000,0000,,{That's no way to talk to \Nthe best on the frontier.}Takhle s nejlepším hraničářem mluvit nebudete.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:09.39,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Come, now, everyone. You mustn't fight.}No tak, všichni. Nemusíte se hádat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:14.38,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{So he's really not going \Nto look at the quests...}Takže se na ty úkoly fakt nepodívá...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:19.29,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{I guess he did say that there's no need \Nto rush, since no one likes goblin-slaying.}Hádám, že se nepotřebuje dívat na tabuli, \Nkdyž nikdo nebere úkoly se zabíjením goblinů.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:22.25,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{Hello.}Zdravím.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:23.06,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Hey.}Hoj.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:25.59,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{A-About the other day...}O-Ohledně minula...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.59,0:10:30.53,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{I still think destroying a cave with \Nflammable liquid is going too far.}Stále si myslím, že zničení jeskyně hořlavinou je už moc.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:32.09,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{What's your point?}A co s tím?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:34.57,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{It's a far better option than \Nletting the goblins live.}Mnohem lepší možnot by byla, nechat gobliny naživu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:38.19,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{Shouldn't you think more about consequences?}Neměl byste víc přemýšlet nad důsledky?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:40.70,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{You might cause an avalanche doing that.}Může to způsobit zával.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:42.61,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{The goblins are a bigger problem.}Goblini jsou větší problém.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:44.23,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{Y-Yes, but...}To ano, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:47.92,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{What I'm trying to say is that \Nyou shouldn't think that way.}Co se snažím říct je to, \Nže byste měl přemýšlet nad jiným způsobem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:48.83,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{I see.}Chápu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:50.36,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{Don't you understand?}Copak to nechápete?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:52.96,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{He said he'd formed a party with \Nsomeone about a month ago, but...}Říkal, že před měsícem s někým utvořil skupinu, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:55.05,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{I guess it was with a girl.}Hádám, že to bylo s touto dívkou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:11:00.15,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{Also, couldn't we use something... \Ndifferent... to cover our scent?}Taky, nemohli bychom použít něco... \Njiného... k zakrytí našeho pachu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:02.87,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Do you remember what time we're attacking?}Pamatuješ si v jaké době útočíme?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:06.06,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{E-Either early morning or early evening...}B-Buď brzy ráno, nebo brzy večer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:09.10,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Now, tell me why.}Teď mi řekni, proč.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:12.40,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{Because early evening for goblins \Nis early morning for us.}Protože brzy večer je pro gobliny brzy ráno pro nás.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:15.56,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Correct. So during their afternoons, \Nor the middle of the night for us,}Správně. \NTakže během odpoledne nebo uprostřed noci pro nás,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:17.11,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{they are the most guarded.}jsou nejvíc stráženi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:20.36,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Next. What are the steps to approach them?}Dál. Jak budeme postupovat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:24.87,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{Um, if possible, light a \Nfire and smoke them out,}Pokud je to možné tak zapálíme oheň a vykouříme je ven,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:27.12,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{because it's dangerous inside their nests.}protože uvnitř jeskyně je to nebezpečné.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.37,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Correct.}Správně.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:32.02,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{The only time we enter a nest is when \Nthere's no other way, we don't have time,}Jediný případ, kdy vstupujeme do hnízda je, \Nkdyž není jiný způsob nebo není čas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:34.31,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{or we're certain we can kill them all.}nebo si nejsme jisti, že je dokážeme všechny zabít.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:35.65,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{All right.}Dobře.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:37.88,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{Huh?}Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:41.51,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Oh, good morning, Goblin Slayer.}Dobré ráno, zabijáku goblinů.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:46.01,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Goblins. Are there any quests?}Goblini. Máte nějaké úkoly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:51.77,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Ah, yes, goblin-slaying.}Jistě, likvidace goblinů.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:53.43,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{We have three quests.}Máme tři úkoly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:55.78,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{One is from a river village in the west,}Jeden je od vesnice u řeky na západě,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:11:58.09,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{one is a small nest in the southern forest,}jedno malé hnízdo v jižním lese,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:12:00.15,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{and one... I guess you could call it an old fort.}a jeden... Hádám, že bychom to mohli nazvat starou pevností.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:03.79,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{It's a mountain castle in \Nthe mountains to the north.}Je to horský hrad na severu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:04.99,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{They've settled there?}Usadili se tam?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:07.66,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Yes, and there have already \Nbeen some casualties.}Ano, už mají nějaké oběti.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:12.16,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{The younger sister of the one who \Nput up the request was kidnapped,}Mladší sestra toho, kdo zadal úkol byla unesena,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:15.56,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{and a wandering adventurer who went \Nto find her hasn't come back yet.}a dobrodruh, který se tam vydal se ještě nevrátil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:18.68,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{It's too late for them, then. \NBut I can't let the goblins live.}Je pro něj moc pozdě. \NAle nemůžu ty gobliny nechat žít.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:21.24,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{If I take them out now, \Nthere shouldn't be further casualties.}Pokud hned vyrazím, neměli by být další oběti.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:24.88,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{We'll be counting on you, then, Goblin Slayer.}Spoléháme na vás, Zabijáku goblinů.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.88,0:12:28.23,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{One question. Did anyone else \Ntake a goblin-slaying quest?}Jedna otázka. Vzal ještě někdo úkol s likvidací goblinů?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:30.93,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Yes, a party of rookies accepted one.}Ano, skupinka nováčků si jeden vzala.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:33.33,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{They took the request from the river village.}Vzali si úkol z vesnice od řeky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:35.55,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Rookies? What was their party like?}Nováčci? Jak jejich parta vypadala?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.16,0:12:42.46,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{One warrior, one wizard, and one priest.}Jeden válečník, mág a kněz.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:44.77,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{They're all porcelain-ranked.}Mají porcelánovou hodnost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:46.63,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Not a bad balance.}To není špatná sestava.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:50.17,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{If it's the three who were in the lobby \Nearlier, they won't be able to handle it!}Ale pokud to byli ti tři z předtím, tak to nezvládnou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:52.22,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{Even my party had four members...}Dokonce i má skupina měla čtyři členy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:54.12,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{I explained that to them, but...}Vysvětlila jsem jim to, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:57.54,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{We can't leave them alone! \NWe have to go save them!}Nemůžeme je opustit, musíme je zachránit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:58.64,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Do as you please.}Dělej jak myslíš.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:12:59.37,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{Huh?}Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:01.56,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm going to destroy the \Nmountain castle in the north.}Jdu zničit horskou pevnost na severu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:03.75,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{Y-You're just going to abandon them?}Opustíte je?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.75,0:13:06.64,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{If you want to go save them, you can.}Pokud je chceš jít zachránit, můžeš.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:10.55,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{But that means you'll be facing \Na horde of goblins on your own!}Ale, to pak budete čelit hordě goblinů sám.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.55,0:13:12.50,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{I've done that many times.}Už jsem to dělal mnohokrát.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:16.70,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{Honestly, I can never get through to you.}Ach jo, vy si nikdy nedáte říct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:17.65,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Are you coming?}Jdeš?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:18.90,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{Yes!}Ano!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:23.34,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm going.}Vyrážím.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:25.29,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Huh? O-Okay.}Co? D-Dobře.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.29,0:13:26.16,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Be careful.}Buď opatrný.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:28.01,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Be careful getting home.}Buď opatrná po cestě domů.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:44.67,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{He didn't come back that day.}Ten den se nevrátil domů.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:46.63,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Or the next day...}Ani další den...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.65,0:13:51.02,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{I wonder if he's still fighting.}Zajímalo by mě, jestli pořád bojuje.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:54.71,Shinsou main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,{You're going to have a hard day \Ntomorrow if you stay up too late.}Když budeš ponocovat, tak tě čeká zítra těžký den.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:58.19,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah. I'll go to bed after \NI wait a little longer.}Jo. Počkám ještě chvilku a půjdu spát.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:31.84,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Think about how it would feel}Zamyslete se nad tím, jaké by to bylo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:34.44,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{if your home was suddenly \Nattacked by monsters...}kdyby váš domov najednou přepadly monstra...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:40.23,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Yes, if your home was suddenly \Nattacked by monsters one day.}Ano, pokud byl váš domov najednou přepaden monstry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:46.49,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{They act as though they own the \Nplace and kill your friends,}Jednali by jako by jim to místo patřilo a zabíjeli vaše přátele,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.95,0:14:48.32,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{kill your family,}zabili by vám rodinu,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.66,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{and plunder the rest of the village.}a vydrancovali vesnici.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:04.32,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Another example would be if \Nyour older sister was attacked,}Dalším příkladem by mohlo být, \Nkdyby napadli vaši starší sestru,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:08.38,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{tormented, made a plaything, then killed...}mučili ji, udělali si z ní hračku a pak zabili...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:13.26,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Let's say that you witnessed \Nall this, from start to finish,}Řekněme, že jste to všechno sledovali od začátku až do konce,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:16.23,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{in hiding as you held your breath...}zatímco jste se skrývali se zatajeným dechem...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:20.98,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{There's no way you'd forgive them.}Neexistuje způsob jak byste jim mohli odpustit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:26.19,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{You would take up weapons and do \Nwhatever you could to get revenge.}Chopili byste se zbraní a udělali, co můžete pro pomstu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:29.95,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{You would hunt them all down and attack them.}Lovili byste je a pozabíjeli.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:33.45,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{You'd kill, kill, and kill even more.}Zabíjet, zabíjet a zabíjet je ještě víc.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.08,0:15:41.44,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Of course, there will be days \Nyou're successful and days you fail.}Samozřejmě byli dny, kdy jste byli úspěšní i neúspěšní.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:45.85,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{You'll try to figure out the \Nbest way to kill them next time.}Snažíte se zlepšit a zabíjet je příště ještě líp.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.85,0:15:48.63,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{You'll think about this for days and months.}Přemýšlíte o tom celé dny a měsíce.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:54.19,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{You'll test every single idea you come up with.}Vyzkoušeli byste každý nápad, který by vás napadl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:58.01,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{As you continue to do that,\Nyou start to enjoy it.}Jak byste v tom pokračovali, začalo by se vám to i zamlouvat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:06.44,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{A kind moron will suggest that \Nyou let the children live,}Nějaký hlupák by pravděpodobně navrhl nechat děti žít,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.37,0:16:12.13,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{with a smug face, not realizing that \Nthese things will attack villages}se samolibým výrazem by si neuvědomil,\N že by začali útočit na vesnice
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:14.37,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{and steal livestock to survive.}a krást dobytek aby přežili.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:17.08,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Young, aspiring adventurers as well as}Jak říkají mladí začínající dobrodruzi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:20.09,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{new, porcelain-ranked adventurers \Nwill confidently say,}na nové porcelánové hodnosti
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.40,0:16:23.45,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{"I chased away a goblin that\Ncame to my village once!"}"Jednou, když do naší vesnice přišel goblin, \Ntak se mi ho podařilo zahnat!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:25.83,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{"They're weak." "They're easy to deal with."}"Jsou slabí. " "Lehce si s něma poradíte."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:29.42,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{The goblin that the proud youth \Nof the village had chased away}Goblin, kterého pyšný mládenec zahnal
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:33.26,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{was no more than a goblin that had been \Nsmoked out and was trying to escape.}nebyl nic víc než právě vykouřený goblin,\N který se snažil utéct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:36.97,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{This gives them confidence, \Nand they become adventurers.}To jim dodá sebevědomí a stanou se dobrodruhy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:41.18,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Meanwhile, the goblins that \Nsurvived and gained experience}Mezitím goblini, kteří přežili a získali zkušenosti
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:43.92,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{become Wanderers and continue to grow.}se stali tuláky a pokračovali v růstu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:47.94,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Eventually, the Wanderers become the \Nleaders or the bodyguards of nests.}Nakonec se z tuláků stali vůdci nebo strážci hnízd.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:53.16,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Which means...}Což znamená...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:56.92,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{I am, in turn, a goblin to them.}Pro ně jsem naopak goblinem já.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:04.90,Shinsou main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,{He's one matter, but you need to remember...}On je jedna věc, ale neměla bys zapomínat...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:08.65,Shinsou main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,{I let him stay here because he pays, \Nbut you shouldn't get involved with him.}Nechávám ho tu jen proto, \Nže platí, ale ty by ses s ním neměla zaplétat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:13.26,Shinsou main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,{I know you were childhood friends, \Nbut now matter how he was in the past...}Vím, že jste byli přátelé z dětství, ale teď...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:18.32,Shinsou main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,{Truth is, right now...}Pravdou je, že už...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:24.06,Shinsou main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,{He's completely lost it.}Je úplně ztracený.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:26.77,Shinsou main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,{You realize that, too, don't you?}Uvědomuješ si to, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:29.11,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Still...}Ještě...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:31.55,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm going to wait a little longer.}Počkám o trochu déle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:34.78,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{That makes five.}To byl pátý.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:38.49,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{They'll be here any minute.}Měli by tu být každým okamžikem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:39.99,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{R-Right!}D-Dobře!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:42.95,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{O merciful Earth Mother,}Milosrdná matko Země,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:48.14,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{please protect us, the weak, \Nwith the powers of the earth.}prosím ochraň nás slabé silou země.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:50.21,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{Protection!}Ochrana!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:02.95,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{I'd heard that you'd been \Ngranted a new miracle.}Slyšel jsem, že ti byl udělen nový zázrak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:06.73,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{That's six.}To je šestý.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:09.27,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Thanks to that, we took care \Nof them pretty quickly.}Díky za to, postarali jsme se o ně dost rychle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:12.71,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{T-To think that I'd be using Protection,}Pomyslet si, že použiji Ochranu,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:16.11,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{the new miracle the merciful Earth \NMother bestowed upon me, like this.}můj nový zázrak, který mi byl udělen milosrdnou matkou Země, zrovna takto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:20.07,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{They might have a back door \Nor an alternate escape route.}Možná mají nějaký zadní východ, nebo jinou cestu k útěku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.47,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't let down your guard.}Nepolevuj v ostražitosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:24.46,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm amazed you could even think of that.}Překvapuje mě, že vás něco takového napadlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.28,0:18:27.28,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Imagination is a weapon.}Představivost je moje zbraň.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.28,0:18:29.23,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Those who lack it are first to die.}Ti, kteří ji postrádají, umírají první.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:33.66,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{Like the ones who dove in before?}Jako ti, kteří vešli dovnitř předtím?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:35.05,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Precisely.}Přesně.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:47.72,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{Great Earth Mother,}Velká matko Země,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:53.71,Shinsou main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,{why did you bestow this miracle upon me?}proč jsi mi udělila tento zázrak?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:06.58,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Now we don't have to put out the fire.}Už si nemusíme dělat starosti s ohněm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:07.61,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Once it goes out,}Jakmile vylezou,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.61,0:19:09.97,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{we're going to hunt down \Nany survivors and kill them.}ulovíme všechny přeživší a pozabíjíme je.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:11.83,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{I won't let a single one survive.}Nenechám ani jednoho naživu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:20.09,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{People may call you a specialist \Nwho only hunts weaklings,}Lidé vás možná nazývají specialistou, který loví pouze slabé,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:23.87,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{but you are doing something \Nthat needs to be done.}ale vy děláte to co je potřeba.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:26.18,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Please be more proud of yourself.}Prosím buďte na sebe více pyšný.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.78,0:19:29.72,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{You're a silver-ranked adventurer.}Máte stříbrnou hodnost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.24,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{As I figured,}Jak jsem předpokládal,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.93,0:19:41.78,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{it's hard to act more like a silver.}je obtížné se chovat jako ostatní na stříbrné hodnosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.76,0:19:54.55,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Good morning, everyone!}Dobré ráno, všem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.55,0:19:57.27,Shinsou main,Guild girl,0000,0000,0000,,{It's time to post all the \Nquests available this morning.}Je čas vyvěsit nově přístupné úkoly pro toto ráno.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.27,0:19:59.04,Shinsou main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{That's what we've been waiting for!}To je na co jsme čekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.79,0:20:19.12,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Welcome back.}Vítej zpět.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.12,0:20:19.74,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah.}Jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.89,0:20:23.45,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Are you hungry?}Jsi hladový?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:25.43,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{Want me to make you something?}Chceš něco připravit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:26.73,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah.}Jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:29.85,Shinsou main,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll make you something extra delicious!}Připravím ti něco extra dobrého.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:31.14,Shinsou main,Goblin slayer,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah.}Jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.29,0:22:11.85,Shinsou main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,{The Goblin Slayer swung swift and true,}Zabiják goblinů švihl rychle a svižně,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:16.15,Shinsou main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,{sending the goblins' heads into the sky.}poslal goblinské hlavy k nebesům.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.15,0:22:19.90,Shinsou main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,{O, behold his blade blazing blue,}Ó, pohleďte na jeho modře planoucí čepel,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:24.66,Shinsou main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,{tempered in true silver,}kalená v pravém stříbře
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.66,0:22:29.44,Shinsou main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,{never betraying its master.}nikdy nezradíc svého pána.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:34.06,Shinsou main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,{Finally, the Goblin King's \Nreign came to an end.}Konečně byla krutovláda krále goblinů u konce.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.06,0:22:37.91,Shinsou main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,{The rescued beautiful maiden \Nleans into our hero.}Zachráněná krásná panna se naklání k našemu hrdinovi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.91,0:22:40.50,Shinsou main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,{However, he is the Goblin Slayer.}Nicméně, je to Zabiják goblinů.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.50,0:22:45.69,Shinsou main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,{He is sworn to wander the \Nland, never to settle down.}Přísahal, že se bude toulat zemí a nikdy se neusadí,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.16,0:22:50.45,Shinsou main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,{The princess reached out her \Nhand, but only grasped air.}Princezna k němu natáhla ruku, ale uchopila jen vzduch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:57.05,Shinsou main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,{But of course, our hero continued \Non his way, never turning around.}Ale jistě, náš hrdina pokračoval na své cestě bez ohlédnutí.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.38,0:23:02.79,Shinsou main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,{From the passage in "Goblin Slayer: \NThe Brave Warrior from the Frontier"}Úryvek ze " Zabiják goblinů: Statečný válečník z hranic."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:04.78,Shinsou main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,{named "The Stronghold Up in Flames."}který se jmenuje "Pevnost v plamenech"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.78,0:23:06.63,Shinsou main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,{Thus ends our tale for now.}To je prozatím konec našeho příběhu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:15.53,Shinsou main,High Elf Archer,0000,0000,0000,,{Hey, that adventurer you \Nwere just singing about...}Hele, ten dobrodruh, o kterém jsi právě zpíval...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.53,0:23:16.94,Shinsou main,High Elf Archer,0000,0000,0000,,{Does he actually exist?}Existuje vůbec?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.94,0:23:19.42,Shinsou main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,{Yes, of course.}Ano, jistě.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.42,0:23:23.49,Shinsou main,Bard,0000,0000,0000,,{You can find him in the frontier city\Nabout two to three days west from here.}Můžeš ho najít v pohraničním městě,\N tři dny odsud na západ.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.85,0:23:24.55,Shinsou main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,{I see.}Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:34.00,Shinsou main,High elf archer,0000,0000,0000,,Orcbolg...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:34.00,Shinsou main,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Orcbolg je jméno, kterým Zabijáka goblinů nazývají elfové a trpaslíci.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.93,0:23:40.23,sign_33927_268_Next_Time,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{Next Time}Příště
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.93,0:23:40.23,sign_33927_269__Goblin_Slayer_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{Unexpected Visitors}Nečekaní návštěvníci
